he RP aspects; makes the characters less amazing/heroic/interesting; pulls you back into reality breaking the enchantment of the fairy tale. Not that I'm much of a roleplayer though. <br>
For some people who are dear friends in game I feel a natural curiousity and a desire to know what kind of people are behind the screen making the game so much fun. This knowledge is not required or needed, however, for me to consider them true friends...<br>
RL or RP its still reality... if it isn't, well, we have all been having a major hallucination for the past 2 years or so...<br>
 <p><center><img src="http://dynamic.gamespy.com/~cazic/cazic/ubb/uploads/mokas.jpg"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23327"><br> Mokas Stardust</a>
</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ublearchie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Blearchie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Benefactor</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/4/02 6:28:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1500.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~jim_howard/sig.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Age</span><hr size=1> EQ isn't a role play game to me. It's a social game. I play because I know the folks behind other toons are real people and not some computer generated AI <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  You'd be amazed what we discuss in /gu. Rarely does it have to do with what's going on in the game <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  The best part is you get a chance to meet folks spread out all over the country or world that you would never know otherwise.<br>
<br>
Classes and races are just choices folks make to have different challenges.<br>
<br>
As far as ages and what you look like, who cares? If I've played with you alot, debated with you, laughed with you, argued with you, I've allready made the decision that I do or don't want you for a friend.<br>
<br>
Eventually EQ will fade away, but the friendships won't. If folks felt otherwise, you wouldn't see the posts about gathering when they discover they are in the same towns and such. <br>
<br>
A good number of my guildmates are in the same town on the west side of the US. I recently worked out some time off and flew up there to hang out for a long weekend. It was some of the best vaccation time I have had in a long while <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
 <p>Blearchie Pooh<BR>
Phantasmist of CoFE</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/urunno1munkey.showPublicProfile?language=EN>runno1munkey</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/4/02 9:00:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1500.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Age</span><hr size=1>  I agree with you Blearchie, the people who i speak with, or play with, ( that i Like...) know my RL name, where im from, my age, what I do and all that, so we dont always talk about the game, or even play the game really =P the only reason today that i ended up grouping is because i've never grouped with a funny little rogue like the one i met (hubbe), but anyway... My days chatting with people all over the place, From Hungarians to Americans, guys, gals, adults, *brats* and all the other kinds of people you can meet on a game like Everquest are great, and being able to put a face behind that person does make it a little nicer too, (If i could get my Camera to work mine would be up too =/) but yeah, i do some what agree with you in some respect, but mostly i wont even worry about it, everyones entitled to their own opinion =) <p><HTML><BODY>
