<br>
I think it is great that you can actually meet someone, begin to build a friendship -- when in real life this might have been a person you never would have even said hello to!  Neatest thing about the net -- there are not so many barriers as we surround ourselves with in the 'real world'.<br>
<br>
Some of my best friends are 15... others are 55.  Wonderful  :) <p><font face="Blackchancery" size=+2>Carabella Valenteen</font><br>Immortal Mercy's port 'ho<br>

